column2: SELECT SpecObj.plate, SpecObj.fiberid, SpecObj.mjd, SpecObj.z, SpecObj.zwarning, emissionLinesPort.Flux_OIII_#, emissionLinesPort.Flux_OIII_#_Err into mydb.portsmuth from SpecObj, emissionLinesPort WHERE emissionLinesPort.Flux_OIII_# > emissionLinesPort.Flux_OIII_#_Err*# AND SpecObj.specobjid = emissionLinesPort.specobjid AND SpecObj.class = # AND SpecObj.zwarning = # AND emissionLinesPort.Flux_OIII_#_Err > #
